Jaytrace: a personal ray tracer project

v0.1

Features
Sphere intersections, reflections

Dependencies
CMake 2.8+
Qt 4.6 (core and test libraries)
Eigen 2.0

Planned features include
* Full transparency (diffraction, total internal reflection, proper handling of shadows)
* support for rendering multiple frames for an animation
* photon mapping
* OpenCL/threading for computation
* network communication to enable multiple machines to work on one output image
* kd-tree based intersection algorithm
* powerful file representation of scenes and objects
